meanings: (국회·지방의회 등의) member of a legislative body[assembly], (Am) assemblyman, assemblywoman, congressman, congresswoman, (Brit) Member of Parliament ((abb.)MP)
(의사) doctor ((abb.)Dr.), (S) doc; (일반 개업의) general practitioner ((abb.)GP); (전문의) specialist; (내과의) physician; (외과의) surgeon
(한국의) member of the National Assembly; (미국의) member of Congress, Congressperson; (영국의) member of Parliament ((abb.)MP)
member of the upper house, (Am) senator, (Brit) member of the House of Lords
